Precisely speaking, I suspended the code are a few minutes and the console threw out the above stack trace. 
Actually, I found the issue. It should be MacOS multiple threading handling issue with OpenCV. 
https://github.com/opencv/opencv/issues/5150
I will try with Ubuntu to see if this is still an issue.
